We should have some sort of machine config that enables/disables phosphor-nvme rather than moving it to be a machine-specific recipe.

Do we want phosphor-nvme disabled on all machines except Bletchley?  Let's just not build it in.
Thank you for correction, I'll try to keep common bbappend and files but remove folders which are named by project.

The SRC_URI line has been changed to optional, also remove the redundant conf.
Thank you for correction.
